summary:
David Tennant To Attend Wales Comic Con In April  

David Tennant has been added to the guest list of Wales Comic Con, taking...
caption:
David Tennant To Attend Wales Comic Con In April 

David Tennant has been added to the guest list of Wales Comic Con, taking place at Glyndwr University in Wrexham on April 27th and 28th. David will be appearing on Saturday 27th only.

The geek-friendly event boasts a host of star guests including Billie Piper, Sean Pertwee, Sam Neill, Rupert Grint, Charlie Cox, Jennifer Morrison, Ron Perlman, Hayley Attwell, Michelle Gomez, Lucy Davis, Andrew Scott, to name but a few. There’s also a Cosplay Masquerade and merchandise for lovers of comics, games, fan art and much more.

See the full guest list here

Ticket information is here - don’t forget you will need to buy both entry and photo tickets!

For more information visit www.walescomiccon.com

summary: What We Learned About Good Omens at SXSW 2019
title: What We Learned About Good Omens at SXSW 2019
excerpt: A peek at the Good Omens experience at SXSW and what fans can expect of the upcoming adaptation.
description:
The Good Omens experience at SXSW 2019 in Austin was a dream. I attended a party where there were sword swallowers, prophecies, and a replica of Aziraphale’s bookshop. @neil-gaiman had an entire session where he discussed writing, adaptations, and more. 

But nothing was quite as exciting as the panel on Saturday night, when writer Neil Gaiman, director Douglas Mackinnon, and cast members David Tennant, Michael Sheen, and Jon Hamm all came together with moderator Aisha Tyler to discuss what it was like to create the upcoming show.

Here are a few of the takeaways—from Aziraphile & Crowley to the expanded character of the angel Gabriel to why the show is so incredibly special.

summary: So I’m re-watching Series 4, and I’ve only just picked up on the fact that Sky Silvestry from Midnight is a lesbian or bisexual...
body:
So I’m re-watching Series 4, and I’ve only just picked up on the fact that Sky Silvestry from Midnight is a lesbian or bisexual and I’m shook?

Look at that an LGBT character who’s LGBTness doesn’t mean their ENTIRE PERSONALITY, take notes Chibnall and Moffat.

direct quote from Midnight

Sky: “I’ve found myself single rather recently, not by choice.”

The Doctor: “What happened?”

Sky: “Oh the usual. She needed her own space, as they say, a different galaxy in fact, I reckon that’s enough space don’t you?”
